make much difference,

00:18:54.710 --> 00:18:57.507
they'll say.
They'll say that the payoff for

00:18:57.507 --> 00:19:01.309
even great base stealers are
attempting to steal or not,

00:19:01.309 --> 00:19:04.956
when you take into account the
