00:22:23.451 --> 00:22:24.930
steal.
It shows up where?

00:22:24.930 --> 00:22:28.236
It shows up in the fact that
the pitching team changes their

00:22:28.236 --> 00:22:31.374
behavior to make it harder for
this guy to steal by going

00:22:31.374 --> 00:22:34.099
faster to the plate,
or throwing more fast balls.

00:22:34.099 --> 00:22:36.049
Where will that show up in the
