00:23:14.043 --> 00:23:15.833
using Game Theory,
we know we're in a mixed

00:23:15.833 --> 00:23:17.891
strategy equilibrium.
We know, in fact,

00:23:17.891 --> 00:23:20.339
the pitching team must be
reacting to it.

00:23:20.339 --> 00:23:24.518
We know there must be a cost in
